sequenceDiagram
    participant John
    participant Alice
    Alice-&amp;gt;&amp;gt;John: Hello John, how are you?
    John--&amp;gt;&amp;gt;Alice: Great!
{% endmermaid %}
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

